<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<h2 id="head-7c617132936d90cda539214301bc21375e5e1e66">The Long Sword of Angmar (4d5) (-22,-25)</h2>
<em>Dark flames wreath the naked steel of the Witch-King of Angmar. A mighty curse to all those who wield it apart from its master, the torture of the wraithworld awaits those who dare.</em> <p>
It decreases your strength, wisdom, charisma and speed by 10. It does extra damage from fire. It drains life from your foes. It makes you invisible. It provides immunity to paralysis. It renders you incorporeal. It allows you to see invisible monsters. It allows you to sense the presence of undead. It slows your metabolism. It prevents teleportation. It aggravates nearby creatures. It is heavily cursed. It carries an ancient morgothian curse. It can clone monsters. 
</p>
